dx + x\,dy = e^{-y} \sec^2y \, dy
=>dx = e^{-y} \sec^2y \, dy - x \, dy
=>dx = (e^{-y} \sec^2y - x) \, dy
=>dx/dy = (e^{-y}) \sec^2y - x 
